             int _eficacia)
        Parameter constructor. Constructs a instance of the CN2 algorithm by copying the configuration parameters given.
        Parameters:
        ftrain - Training dataset filename
        feval - Validation dataset filename.
        ftest - Test dataset filename.
        fSalidaTr - Training output filename.
        fSalidaTst - Test output filename.
        fsal - Global output filename.
        tamEstrella - maximum size of the star for the beam search.
        _nu - nu parameter for multiplication weight.
        _seCubre - minimum percentage of examples of a class to consider it as covered.
        _multi - type of weight update (1 multiplication, 0 summation).
        _eficacia - flag effective of efficient.
